man : https://www.opennet.ru/man.shtml?topic=curl&category=1&russian=3

curl -i localhost (headers & body)
curl -v localhost (full)

curl  -X POST -F 'image=~/Desktop/1.png' localhost (image ?)
curl localhost -o kek (write response to a file, like '>' in bash)



